Position: Senior Cloud DevOps Engineer (Contract) 6 months rolling  
  
Location: Brisbane (Hybrid Working)  
  
Duration: Contract  
  
We are seeking a highly skilled Senior Cloud DevOps Engineer for a contract
position based in Brisbane. The ideal candidate will have over 5 years of
extensive experience with Terraform and a solid understanding of both Azure
and GCP cloud platforms.  
  
The role will primarily involve setting up CI/CD pipelines and optimising
cloud infrastructure. Knowledge of Kubernetes, particularly with AKS and GKE,
is preferred. This is an excellent opportunity for a talented individual to
contribute to cutting-edge projects in a hybrid working environment.  
  
Requirements:  
  
5+ years of experience with Terraform.  
Proficiency in both Azure and/or GCP cloud platforms.  
Experience setting up CI/CD pipelines.  
Working knowledge of Kubernetes, preferably with AKS and GKE.  
Strong problem-solving skills and ability to work independently.  
Excellent communication and collaboration skills.  
Prior experience in a similar role.  
  
If you are passionate about cloud technologies and possess the necessary
expertise, we encourage you to apply for this exciting opportunity. Join our
dynamic team and play a key role in driving innovation and success in the
cloud space.

